Name: Brick Breaker Premium
About the game: The classic brick-breaker game. It's Back! You are the hero “Blippy” the paddle, that has to save planet Earth from it's greatest threat. Can you finish the game and save Earth from “The Evil Snarfer”?... - 35 Challenging Levels to Complete. - Heroic Storyline, Where It All Began! - Gamepad Support. - Classic Power-ups. - See Ending Cutscenes If You Can Complete The Game!!! It's Addictive and Loads of Fun! Good Luck!
